> Module Eligibility
> Using Exclusion_chain

# Eligibility

Alaska Medicaid income eligibility determination based on adjusted earned income after exclusions. Applies the APA 10-step exclusion chain to both client-stated and DOL-reported income, checks reasonable compatibility (523B), and determines eligibility against the Expanded Refused Cash Income Limits.

Module: `Eligibility` | Version: `2026Q1` | Effective: 2026-01-01 | Jurisdiction: State (US, AK)

DO NOT EDIT — regenerate with: `python tools/transpile_to_catala.py ak_doh/specs/eligibility.civil.yaml ak_doh/output/eligibility.catala_en --scope EligibilityDecision`

## Declarations

#### gross_earned_income

Client-stated gross monthly earned income before any exclusions

*Source: 441-1 EARNED INCOME*

#### federal_exclusions

Total income excluded by federal law applicable to earned income (pre-aggregated from 442-3A list)

*Source: 442-2A — Earned Income Exclusions Authorized by Federal Laws*

#### eitc_exclusion

EITC advance or Child Tax Credit payment received this month

*Source: 442-2B — Earned Income Tax Credit and Child Tax Credit Payments*

#### irregular_earned_income

Client-stated infrequent or irregular earned income this month (subject to $10/month exclusion)

*Source: 442-1A — Infrequent/Irregular Income; 442-2C — Infrequent/Irregular Earned Income*

#### student_earned_income

Client-stated earned income of a blind or disabled student under age 22 attending school regularly

*Source: 442-2D — Student Earned Income Exclusion*

#### student_monthly_limit

Monthly maximum for student earned income exclusion (Addendum 1, indexed annually; e.g. $2,410 for 2026)

*Source: Addendum 1 PROGRAM STANDARDS — Student Earned Income Exclusion*

#### non_needs_based_unearned_remainder

Unused portion of the $20/month general income exclusion after applying to non-needs-based unearned income; applied to earned income in step 5

*Source: 442-1B — $20 Per Month General Income Exclusion*

#### impairment_work_expenses

Verified impairment-related work expenses for a disabled individual

*Source: 442-2G — Impairment Related Work Expenses for Disabled*

#### blind_work_expenses

Verified work expenses of a blind individual

*Source: 442-2I — Work Expenses for the Blind*

#### self_support_exclusion

Earned income used to fulfill an SSA- or DVR-approved plan for achieving self-support

*Source: 442-1C — Amount to Fulfill a Plan for Achieving Self-Support*

#### household_type

Household type code used to look up the applicable income standard (e.g. A1E, B1E, H1E, A2S, NHR)

*Source: Addendum 1 (ADLTC) — Expanded Refused Cash Income Limits*

#### benefit_year

Calendar year for which income limits apply (e.g. 2026); used to select the correct column in the income limits table

*Source: Addendum 1 (ADLTC) — Expanded Refused Cash Income Limits*

#### dol_earned_income_available

True when DOL electronic wage data is available for this client; false when no DOL history exists (e.g. new job, self-employment not reported to DOL)

*Source: 523B — Reasonable Compatibility action 5*

#### dol_quarterly_earnings

Most recent quarter of earnings reported by DOL and Workforce Development

*Source: 523B — Reasonable Compatibility*

#### gross_earned_income

DOL monthly gross earned income — must be pre-set to dol_quarterly_earnings / 3 by the calling system before invocation

*Source: 523B — Reasonable Compatibility*

#### federal_exclusions

Same as ClientData.federal_exclusions — identical exclusion inputs used for DOL comparison run

*Source: 442-2A — Earned Income Exclusions Authorized by Federal Laws; 523B*

#### eitc_exclusion

Same as ClientData.eitc_exclusion

*Source: 442-2B; 523B*

#### irregular_earned_income

Same as ClientData.irregular_earned_income

*Source: 442-1A; 523B*

#### student_earned_income

Same as ClientData.student_earned_income

*Source: 442-2D; 523B*

#### student_monthly_limit

Same as ClientData.student_monthly_limit

*Source: Addendum 1; 523B*

#### non_needs_based_unearned_remainder

Same as ClientData.non_needs_based_unearned_remainder

*Source: 442-1B; 523B*

#### impairment_work_expenses

Same as ClientData.impairment_work_expenses

*Source: 442-2G; 523B*

#### blind_work_expenses

Same as ClientData.blind_work_expenses

*Source: 442-2I; 523B*

#### self_support_exclusion

Same as ClientData.self_support_exclusion

*Source: 442-1C; 523B*

```catala-metadata
declaration enumeration HouseholdType:
  -- A1E
  -- B1E
  -- H1E
  -- A2S
  -- B2S
  -- H2S
  -- A2C
  -- B2C
  -- H2C
  -- NHR

declaration enumeration Eligible:
  -- Approve
  -- Deny
  -- ManualVerification

declaration structure ClientData:
  data gross_earned_income content money
  data federal_exclusions content money
  data eitc_exclusion content money
  data irregular_earned_income content money
  data student_earned_income content money
  data student_monthly_limit content money
  data non_needs_based_unearned_remainder content money
  data impairment_work_expenses content money
  data blind_work_expenses content money
  data self_support_exclusion content money
  data household_type content HouseholdType
  data benefit_year content integer

declaration structure DOLRecord:
  data dol_earned_income_available content boolean
  data dol_quarterly_earnings content money
  data gross_earned_income content money
  data federal_exclusions content money
  data eitc_exclusion content money
  data irregular_earned_income content money
  data student_earned_income content money
  data student_monthly_limit content money
  data non_needs_based_unearned_remainder content money
  data impairment_work_expenses content money
  data blind_work_expenses content money
  data self_support_exclusion content money

declaration enumeration ReasonCode:
  -- IncomeExceedsStandardBoth
  -- IncomeExceedsStandardClientOnly

declaration structure ReasonEntry:
  data triggered content boolean
  data code content ReasonCode

declaration scope EligibilityDecision:
  input client_data content ClientData
  input d_o_l_record content DOLRecord
  internal manual_verification_required condition
  internal deny_rule_1_triggered condition
  internal deny_rule_2_triggered condition
  internal all_reason_entries content list of ReasonEntry
  # ── Computed outputs ──
  output client_result scope Exclusion_chain.ExclusionChainDecision
  output dol_result scope Exclusion_chain.ExclusionChainDecision
  output dol_avg_monthly_income content money
  output is_compatible content boolean
  output income_limit content money
  # ── Decisions ──
  output eligible content Eligible
  output reasons content list of ReasonCode
```

## Subscope Wiring

#### client_result

Exclusion chain applied to client-stated income

*Source: 442-4 — Order of Exclusions; 523B*

```catala
scope EligibilityDecision:
  definition client_result.gross_earned_income equals client_data.gross_earned_income
  definition client_result.federal_exclusions equals client_data.federal_exclusions
  definition client_result.eitc_exclusion equals client_data.eitc_exclusion
  definition client_result.irregular_earned_income equals client_data.irregular_earned_income
  definition client_result.student_earned_income equals client_data.student_earned_income
  definition client_result.student_monthly_limit equals client_data.student_monthly_limit
  definition client_result.non_needs_based_unearned_remainder equals client_data.non_needs_based_unearned_remainder
  definition client_result.impairment_work_expenses equals client_data.impairment_work_expenses
  definition client_result.blind_work_expenses equals client_data.blind_work_expenses
  definition client_result.self_support_exclusion equals client_data.self_support_exclusion

```

#### dol_result

Exclusion chain applied to DOL-averaged monthly income for reasonable compatibility comparison

*Source: 523B — Reasonable Compatibility; 442-4 — Order of Exclusions*

```catala
scope EligibilityDecision:
  definition dol_result.gross_earned_income equals d_o_l_record.gross_earned_income
  definition dol_result.federal_exclusions equals d_o_l_record.federal_exclusions
  definition dol_result.eitc_exclusion equals d_o_l_record.eitc_exclusion
  definition dol_result.irregular_earned_income equals d_o_l_record.irregular_earned_income
  definition dol_result.student_earned_income equals d_o_l_record.student_earned_income
  definition dol_result.student_monthly_limit equals d_o_l_record.student_monthly_limit
  definition dol_result.non_needs_based_unearned_remainder equals d_o_l_record.non_needs_based_unearned_remainder
  definition dol_result.impairment_work_expenses equals d_o_l_record.impairment_work_expenses
  definition dol_result.blind_work_expenses equals d_o_l_record.blind_work_expenses
  definition dol_result.self_support_exclusion equals d_o_l_record.self_support_exclusion

```

